---
import { Image } from "astro:assets"
import badge from "../images/badge.svg"
import sustaina from "../images/Sustainable.svg"
import invention from "../images/innovation.svg"
---
<section class=" min-h-svh w-9/12 mx-auto text-white mt-20">
        <h2 class=" text-center text-lg">Why Choose Us:</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-col space-y-2 lg:space-y-0 lg:flex-row items-stretch justify-center mt-10 lg:space-x-6  md:pt-10">
            <div class="text-white text-3xl flex flex-col space-y-6  rounded-3xl p-6 sm:min-h-[200px] w-full lg:w-1/3">
                <Image src={badge} width={50} alt=" image for badge" />
                    <div class="flex flex-col space-y-2">
                        <span class=" text-left text-xl"> Proven Track Record of Excellence</span>
                        <span class=" text-gray-400 text-sm text-left">With a solid track record of excellence in the construction industry, Econo is the trusted choice for customers seeking reliability, quality, and professionalism. We have successfully completed a wide range of projects across various sectors, earning a reputation for delivering exceptional results on time and within budget.</span>
                    </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-white text-3xl flex flex-col space-y-6  rounded-3xl p-6 sm:min-h-[200px] w-full lg:w-1/3">
                <Image src={invention} width={50} alt=" image for innovation" />
                    <div class="flex flex-col space-y-2">
                        <span class=" text-left text-xl">Innovation in Construction Solutions</span>
                        <span class=" text-gray-400 text-sm text-left">We strive to stay ahead of the curve and deliver innovative solutions that set your projects apart. When you choose us, you're choosing a partner who is dedicated to bringing the latest innovations to your construction endeavors, ensuring success now and in the future.</span>
                    </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-white text-3xl flex flex-col space-y-6  rounded-3xl p-6 sm:min-h-[200px] w-full lg:w-1/3">
                <Image class=" " src={sustaina} width={50} alt=" image for sustainability" />
                    <div class="flex flex-col space-y-2">
                        <span class=" text-left text-xl">Commitment to Sustainability</span>
                        <span class=" text-gray-400 text-sm text-left">Sustainability is at the heart of everything we do at Econo. We recognize the importance of minimizing the environmental impact of construction activities and are dedicated to implementing sustainable practices throughout our operations.</span>
                    </div>
            </div>
        </div>
</section>